originalText.text:
I was in need of the FLYEST natural beauty MUA in Harlem, and my luckiest stars landed me in Aundra's chair‚ÄºÔ∏è Boy was I SUPER happy to have picked the right artist‚ÄºÔ∏è

Aundra is skilled far beyond anything I've ever experienced before. The blends, the direction, the patience, the compliments on both her enjoying her passion of the craft + the beauty of the client was such FANTASTIC energy to be surrounded by. The pic speaks for itself, BEAT TO THE GAWDS, HUNTEY‚ÄºÔ∏è Glammed EXACTLY as she's advertised herself to be, a Bare Beauty Goddess‚ÄºÔ∏è üíõ

Aundra was also very communicative and a genuine good spirit. She took her time with me and never made me feel rushed. I had a 10:30 am appointment, and communicated that I needed a look that would last me through the whole day for a wedding and a volunteer event. Aundra then proceeded to make my face sweat-proof, LITERALLY‚ÄºÔ∏è Not a singleeee smudge by the end of my night at 1 am‚ÄºÔ∏è After each step of application, Aundra informed me of what she was applying, she made sure I was comfortable, and even provided comparison tips of other products that other MUAs would use vs what she was using. The analyst in me extremely appreciated the detail‚ÄºÔ∏è

I would have never even known I could look like that if it weren't for you, Aundra‚ÄºÔ∏è Appreciate your talents and thank you for the lovely pictures you provided‚ÄºÔ∏è Can't wait to sit in your chair again soon‚ÄºÔ∏è üíõ
